What’s new in Version 6.0
We listened to your feedback! This release includes print selection enhancements:
• Save time and shipping cost by placing mixed size print orders! After you select photos for print, you can add and change sizes of each one.
• See a summary of your print selections by tapping on the number of prints at the top of the screen, before proceeding to checkout.

Thank you and please keep the feedback coming. We love to hear from you!

Announcing CARDS in the Snapfish app, just in time for the holidays! Now you can create beautiful, personalized 5x7 stationery flat cards for the holidays, birthdays, weddings, and more!
 
Features:
• Choose from thousands of card designs, with design on back of card
• Personalize the front of your card with photos and text
• Easily drag and drop photos into your card design
• Printed on durable, smooth 110lb. stationery cardstock
• Sold in sets of 20 cards and envelopes
• Access photos from your Snapfish account, Facebook, Instagram, iCloud, and camera roll
 
In the next couple of weeks we will be releasing more features for cards, so please stay tuned and let us know what you think!

And don’t forget, you can still order prints and create beautiful photo gifts like canvases, mugs, blankets, pillows, tote bags, and much more!

- Cards - now you can:
     - Edit your photo card from the cart by tapping on the pencil icon. You can save your card to your cart and return later to make any edits before checking out.
     - Brightness/contrast - adjust the brightness and contrast of your photos while creating your photo card for this holiday season!
     - Thumbnail in cart - improved thumbnail to show you the exact design of the card that you added to you cart. 
- Other stability and performance improvements

- CARDS - customize the back of your holiday card! Select from several photo and text layouts to add your own personal touch to the back of your card. Plenty of room to write a custom message to your family and friends! Just flip your card and then select 'color & layout' to view and select from the various back of card layouts.
- CARDS - we have added product detail and pricing information in the cards builder, just tap on the 'i' icon after selecting your card design to see both.
- PRINTS & GIFTS - we have also added product detail information in the prints and gifts builder, just tap on the 'i' icon after selecting your gift to see customization tips and product material/product care information. 
- Improved messaging to show which coupons and credits have been applied to your order during checkout.
